            "title": "澄天獲內地客斥514萬購 呎價約1.79萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"澄天獲內地客斥514萬購，呎價約1.79萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0b5e25429f2afbf19b8764622fd3e9d9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021918405217449.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">澄天獲內地客斥514萬購，呎價約1.79萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英皇國際發展的香港仔新盤澄天已屆現樓階段，近日港股重拾升勢，樓市逐步回復熾熱，項目自上周日起3日分別錄得3宗成交，合共套現逾逾1,500萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>最新一宗成交為昨日售出的15樓B室，面積287方呎，屬1房戶型。買家為內地客人，專程從上海來港到現樓參觀，被項目的南區獨有海景景致及周邊配套等優勢吸引，瞬即簽約落實成交，並斥資514.59萬元購入單位，呎價17,930元，是次入市將作長線投資用途，預計租務回報率可逾4厘。\n\n</p>\n<p>澄天至今沽出 85伙，佔整體項目逾77%，合共套現逾5.29億元。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
